Hello,

it is my second map after lol_lasergame.

This map is better than thirst map because is must finished.

Special thanks a Cortexd mappeur of fy_laserquest in cs 1.6 for take me *.rmf and texture of this map.

specificity :

- 24 slots ( but better play 7 vs 7 )

- only cut and P90 with 2 recharges

- unique style map 

- good optimisation ( with func_occluder, aero portal, buildcubemaps ... ) turn at more 200 fps ^^ in server

- better gameplay with plugin MB_tracer de MBchrono.

*.rar : Maps ( *.bsp and *.res ) ; Textures ; sound ... tested and approuved on the loosersOnLine serveur !!! ;)

Enjoy !!! ;) 

Edit : new *.bsp with 45 sec kill afk ( before is 60 sec ) and block_bullet in glass in arme_room.
